data.description:
This Grant Park condo on the 3rd floor is in a quiet location overlooking trees and a courtyard with skyline view, not the freeway. Easy access to ground floor if needed. Beautiful finishes throughout including a serving buffet with display shelves in dining area, and built in cabinets in living room. Hardwood floors in large living and dining room with open concept kitchen that is outstanding with GE café series appliances including a double oven. Balcony is accessible from living room and primary bedroom, and includes both gas
| and electric hook ups for outdoor grilling. Recently updated with wool carpet/hypoallergenic in both
bedrooms, and new blinds. Hall storage closet is just steps away. Amenities are a “10” and include party room, fitness facilities, indoor pool with whirlpool and sauna, guest suite, business center, conference room, package receiving station. Dog walk area- dog park nearby. Walk to Orchestra Hall, Guthrie theater, Mississippi.  Assumable low interest VA loan.
